Rating: 4
This is very easy to prepare and can be made in much less time that the 45 minutes suggested. It is great as a first course with wine, because it is a salad that does not contain vinegar. It is worth buying the best gorgonzola you can find. Delicious. Even my 14 year old daughter loved it.

