Rating: 0
My guests raved about this salad. When the dressing was done, it seemed to have way too much shallot in it. i strained it, and added about 2 Tbs. of the sauted shallots back into the dressing. it was plenty shalloty I think. i dispensed with the fancy presentation,put it all together in a bowl, much easier, still pretty.

Rating: 2
